{"tid":1381124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求香城online admin新增範圍/合體攻擊武器 - 麻繩","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:47:42.000Z","uid":62776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c4fdb1bf426a70cef46b100255754d8f2ecb212","tid":1381124,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"現在既武器同防具入面<br />\n大多都係一對一用<br />\n但我方玩家既優勢<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人數</span></span>!!!<br />\n<br />\n咁點解推薦 麻繩 做武器呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 中距離武器<br />\n<br />\n唔洗個個都係最前線<br />\n第2，3排既手足都可以使用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 變化多端<br />\n<br />\n繩可以有好多用途<br />\n- 套索<br />\n- 加工(綁搭棚竹)做絆腳器<br />\n- 屬性化 (半截浸油，跟住大家自己諗到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 協力工具<br />\n<br />\n大家可以一齊拉<br />\n套得住狗<br />\n有返4，5個人拉佢就肯定落單<br />\n就算絆腳<br />\n有返10個8個第3，4排既手足拉<br />\n已經靠拆散佢地攻擊<br />\n後排又可以出更多力<br />\n<br />\n但範圍武器<br />\n特別有屬性時要小心TK<br />\n希望admin加入新武器<br />\n應該最近高lv左既野生犬隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5d1a1a3ab50b6105b10831fd8fb2c46cd2ebd1","tid":1381124,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1671901aa91bb45831a601490c1abf1f1b867227","tid":1381124,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"4e30c62fbea2977721a73ac2656d42ce385c972f","tid":1381124,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"897be4beb47d4f107c6b493fcfee294e92f5555d","tid":1381124,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"35b92831816be7489dd23716cb588e91b49b7b11","tid":1381124,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}